{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be secure and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Secure Smart Home</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #2b6cb0; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #bee3f8; /* Light Blue */\n            --text-color: #1a202c; /* Dark Gray */\n            --background-color: #ffffff; /* White */\n            --accent-color: #a0aec0; /* Muted Gray */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #bee3f8 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\"><path fill=\"%232b6cb0\" fill-opacity=\"1\" d=\"M0,160L48,160C96,160,192,160,288,138.7C384,117,480,75,576,85.3C672,96,768,160,864,197.3C960,235,1056,245,1152,218.7C1248,192,1344,128,1392,96L1440,64L1440,0L1392,0C1344,0,1248,0,1152,0C1056,0,960,0,864,0C768,0,672,0,576,0C480,0,384,0,288,0C192,0,96,0,48,